In addition to the good comments you&#39;ve already received from Mike and
Subbu, one other detail to consider is this:  you do not *have* to use
different URIs for order processing in order to process two different media
types.  It is also reasonable to have the same URI handle both (presumably
doing a media type specific conversion to internal data structures, followed
by common processing that doesn&#39;t care what the incoming format was).

Craig McClanahan

